EmergencyContact - Class in blue.mdc.event
Emergency Contact class create a pane and adds text fields to the pane asking for: Name Last Name Relationship Phone Email Address City Zip Code Also it has a button to add emergency contact information of the student, and a SAVE button to save the information to the database
